snippet.title: something went wrong
snippet.description:
this was a remake teaser for REFLEXIA: PROTOTYPE VER. 

in the time that has passed since the release of this video, a lot has changed in the project.. therefore, all content presented here can be considered irrelevant

however, the remake already has a page on Steam! you can add the game to wishlist & make me happier here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2271570/REFLEXIA_THE_ARCHETYPES_ROOM_OF_THREE_WALLS/
 
thank you!

and by the way AUTHOR OF TEASER'S OST: Nikita Kryukov
